  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q65",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q65\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta por factor común\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considere la siguiente ecuación cuadrática incompleta:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>+</mo>\n          <mn>5</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al factorizar por factor común y aplicar la propiedad del producto nulo, ¿cuál es el conjunto solución de la ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n            <mtext> y </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 65
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q66",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q66\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática factorizada en contexto de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento, el tiempo transcurrido, medido en segundos, se representa con la variable <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> y satisface la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></p>\n    <p>¿Cuáles son los posibles valores de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> que cumplen esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math> solamente.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 66
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q67",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\" identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q67\" title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática en contexto de temperatura\" adaptive=\"false\" time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento de laboratorio, la variación de temperatura <em>x</em> (en °C) de una sustancia está relacionada con el tiempo mediante la ecuación\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál es el conjunto solución de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        La única solución es <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Las soluciones son <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        Las soluciones son <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        La única solución es <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 67
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q68",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q68\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con contexto de dinero\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Una emprendedora calcula la ganancia mensual, en miles de pesos, que obtiene al vender cierto producto digital. Para ello utiliza el modelo:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1,2</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>0,5</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo></mo>\n            <mn>30</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Usando la propiedad del producto nulo, cue1l es el conjunto solucif3n de esta ecuacif3n?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>;</mo>\n            <mn>60</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>60</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>;</mo>\n            <mo></mo>\n            <mn>60</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>;</mo>\n            <mn>15</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 68
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q69",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q69\"\n    title=\"Factorización de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracciones\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento de laboratorio, la posición de una partícula en función del tiempo x (en segundos) se modela mediante una ecuación que, luego de simplificar, queda como:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Para resolver la ecuación, una estudiante decide factorizar el lado izquierdo por factor común.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones corresponde a esa factorización?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>=</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>+</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 69
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q70",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q70\"\n    title=\"Ecuación cuadrática y tamaño de muestra en encuesta\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un curso de un colegio se aplicó una encuesta sobre hábitos de estudio. El número \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> de estudiantes que respondieron la encuesta satisface la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac>\n          <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Sabiendo que al menos un estudiante respondió la encuesta, ¿cuántos estudiantes respondieron?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">0 estudiantes.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">5 estudiantes.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">20 estudiantes.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></mrow></math> estudiante.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 70
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q71",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q71\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto tabular\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En una fábrica se registra, para distintos valores de\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>\n      (en cientos de unidades producidas), la función\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>\n      que representa la variación (en unidades) respecto de la meta de producción. Valores negativos indican que se produce menos de lo esperado. Algunos datos se resumen en la tabla:</p>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Cantidad producida\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>\n            (cientos de unidades)</th>\n          <th>Variación\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>V</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math>\n            (unidades)</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>1</td>\n          <td>-108</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>3</td>\n          <td>-216</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>5</td>\n          <td>-180</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>El modelo que ajusta estos datos es\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>V</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>18</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>126</mn><mi>x</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n      Si se desea que la variación sea igual a 0, ¿cuáles son los posibles valores de\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>\n      que satisfacen la ecuación\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>18</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>126</mn><mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> o </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n            <mtext> o </mtext>\n            <mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>7</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 71
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q72",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q72\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto de tiempo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Al estudiar los horarios de llegada de un bus, una estudiante obtiene la siguiente ecuación, donde <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>t</mi></math> representa el tiempo, en horas, transcurrido desde que el bus sale del terminal:\n    <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>0,5</mn><mi>t</mi>\n        <mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>)</mo>\n        <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Usando la propiedad del producto nulo, ¿cuál es el conjunto solución de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 72
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q73",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q73\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracciones\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un laboratorio se estudia la longitud <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> (en metros) de una varilla metálica al calentarse.</p>\n    <p>Para cierta temperatura, la longitud <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> cumple la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál es el conjunto solución en <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>&#x211D;</mi></math> de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>{</mo>\n              <mn>0</mn>\n              <mo>}</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>{</mo>\n              <mn>6</mn>\n              <mo>}</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>{</mo>\n              <mn>0</mn>\n              <mo>;</mo>\n              <mn>6</mn>\n              <mo>}</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <p>\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>{</mo>\n              <mn>0</mn>\n              <mo>;</mo>\n              <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n              <mn>6</mn>\n              <mo>}</mo>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 73
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q74",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q74\"\n    title=\"Altura de una pelota y ecuación cuadrática\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un experimento de f\tsica, la altura <em>h</em> (en metros) de una pelota lanzada verticalmente hacia arriba desde el suelo, en funci\tn del tiempo <em>t</em> (en segundos), se modela por la expresi\tn:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>h</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4,9</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>14,7</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow></math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>Para determinar en qu\t instantes la pelota est\t en el suelo se resuelve la ecuaci\tn:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4,9</mn><msup><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>14,7</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>\tCu\tl es el conjunto soluci\tn de esta ecuaci\tn?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>;</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>{</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>}</mo></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 74
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q75",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q75\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta en contexto estadístico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un estudio estadístico sobre el tiempo de uso diario del celular, se obtiene un modelo en el que los valores posibles de un parámetro <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> deben satisfacer la siguiente ecuación:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál es el conjunto solución en <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>&#x211D;</mi></math> de esta ecuación?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>;</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n            <mo>;</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>{</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>}</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 75
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q76",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\" identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q76\" title=\"Resolución de ecuaciones cuadráticas incompletas por factor común\" adaptive=\"false\" time-dependent=\"false\"><qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\"><qti-correct-response><qti-value>B</qti-value></qti-correct-response></qti-response-declaration><qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body><p>Considere la ecuación <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>. Al factorizarla extrayendo factor común, ¿cuál de las siguientes igualdades es correcta?</p><qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\"><qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></qti-simple-choice></qti-choice-interaction></qti-item-body><qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/></qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 76
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q77",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q77\"\n    title=\"Detección de error en factorización de ecuación cuadrática incompleta\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Un te9cnico este1 calibrando un sensor de presif3n. La diferencia <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></math> (en kPa) entre la presif3n que marca el sensor y la presif3n real se modela mediante</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>D</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>.</p>\n    <p>Para encontrar los valores de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> para los cuales la diferencia es cero, se plantea la ecuacif3n <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>. Un estudiante desarrolla el siguiente procedimiento:</p>\n    <ol>\n      <li><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math></li>\n      <li><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></li>\n      <li>Luego aplica la propiedad del producto nulo y concluye que <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>, por lo tanto <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></math>.</li>\n    </ol>\n    <p>bfCue1l de las siguientes afirmaciones describe correctamente el error cometido por el estudiante?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        El factor comfan extraeddo es incorrecto; en lugar de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> debif3 extraer <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        El binomio entre pare9ntesis este1 mal escrito, porque al desarrollar <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></math> se obtiene <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math> y no <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn><mi>x</mi></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        La aplicacif3n de la propiedad del producto nulo es incorrecta, porque de <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> no se puede concluir <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> o <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        La solucif3n <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></math> no es ve1lida en esta situacif3n de mediciones, por lo que solo corresponde considerar <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mrow></math>.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 77
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q78",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-ALG-06-01_Q78\"\n    title=\"Resolución de ecuación cuadrática incompleta con fracciones y restricción\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considera la siguiente ecuación cuadrática incompleta:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Si se sabe que \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mi>x</mi>\n      </math>\n      es un número real distinto de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mn>0</mn>\n      </math>, ¿cuál es el valor de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mi>x</mi>\n      </math>?\n    </p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mo>&#x2212;</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mn>0</mn>\n        </math>\n        y\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 78
    }
  ]
